head_commit.message:
feat(axvirtio): add console support and update device configurations

- Add axvirtio-console package to support virtual console functionality
- Update Cargo.lock and Cargo.toml to include new dependency
- Modify device configuration in arceos-aarch64.toml to support two virtio_mmio devices
- Remove arceos-aarch64_2.toml configuration file
